2026-04-04 00:04:57 - action_executor - INFO - Executing action: write_code with parameters: {'target': 'agent.py', 'content': 'class SimpleAgent:\n    def __init__(self, name):\n        self.name = name\n        self.memory = {}\n    \n    def learn(self, key, value):\n        self.memory[key] = value\n    \n    def recall(self, key):\n        return self.memory.get(key)\n    \n    def forget(self, key):\n        if key in self.memory:\n            del self.memory[key]\n        \n# Create an instance of the agent\nagent = SimpleAgent("My Agent")\n\n# Teach the agent something\nagent.learn("hello", "world")\n\n# Ask the agent to recall what it learned\nprint(agent.recall("hello"))\n\n# Ask the agent to forget what it learned\nagent.forget("hello")\n\n# Try to recall what the agent forgot\nprint(agent.recall("hello"))\n'}
